REDEYE GAMING DAY JUNE 4th, 2020

Hi Emil!

Once again, it’s time for the annual Redeye Gaming Day.

The event will offer updated insights and presentations from the most influential names in the gaming industry. Due to Covid-19 restrictions, the event will be broadcasted as a live video conference.

As in previous years, the event attracts gaming companies from both the Nordics and continental Europe. The event will be valuable by hearing updated insights from within the gaming industry and discover attractive investment opportunities.

Our ambition is to keep the program time efficient and each presentation will, therefore, consist of 10 minutes presentation by company management followed by 5 minutes Q&A. Questions can be sent before and during the company presentation. Redeye analyst will moderate the Q&A session which will also include questions from the audience watching online.

Below is a summary of the date and time.

Date: Thursday, June 4, 2020
Time: 13:00-17:00
Venue: Online link

Web site: [Gaming Day 2020](https://www.redeye.se/events#/event/585123)

